{"tid":1588643,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蝙蝠俠80週年 13座城市照出蝙蝠信號","createTime":"2019-09-23T02:09:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T05:23:36.000Z","uid":184679,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9f3eb5e777a4029afcd21aff51949652178d269f","tid":1588643,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T02:09:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2019-09-22/900/20190922001961.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2019-09-22%2F900%2F20190922001961.jpg&h=c243aa0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蒙特婁的蝙蝠信號。(圖/美聯社)<br />\n<br />\n美聯社報導，DC漫畫公司正在展開「慶祝蝙蝠俠」的活動，以紀念布魯斯&middot;韋恩（Bruce Wayne）以及其蒙面身份的出現80週年。世界各地13座城市的蝙蝠俠迷們，在週六晚間以自製的「蝙蝠信號燈」點亮，以紀念這個最出名的超級英雄。<br />\n<br />\n蝙蝠俠是DC漫畫公司旗下最著名的超級英雄，第一篇以蝙蝠俠為主角的漫畫，是1939年5月於《偵探漫畫》首次登場，因此今年是蝙蝠俠問世的80週年。不過DC選擇9月舉行慶祝活動，於是粉絲聚會在世界各地都有舉行，其中最有趣的是是許多城市串連，在大廈上打出蝙蝠信號的照明燈。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2019-09-22/900/20190922001960.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2019-09-22%2F900%2F20190922001960.jpg&h=0ee9aa95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n洛杉磯的蝙蝠信號。(圖/美聯社)<br />\n<br />\n第一個裝設蝙蝠信號的城市是澳洲墨爾本的美聯儲廣場，之後還出現在其他13個城市中，包括東京、柏林、羅馬、巴黎、倫敦、蒙特婁、聖保羅和約翰尼斯堡，另外，紐約市的多米諾糖精煉廠公園也有。<br />\n<br />\n洛杉磯還舉辦了粉絲音樂會，和《蝙蝠俠》首映式的5公里馬拉松跑步活動，許多人都裝扮成漫畫角色一起同樂。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2019-09-22/900/20190922001955.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2019-09-22%2F900%2F20190922001955.jpg&h=7f849834&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n墨西哥城舉行的蝙蝠俠慶祝會(圖/美聯社)<br />\n<br />\n與其他超級英雄不同，蝙蝠俠是個沒有超能力的人類，他所有的才能來自於裝備、道具與敏銳的智慧，不過更直接的講法是「有錢」。大銀幕的蝙蝠俠電影，自1989年提姆波頓版以來，已歷經了10部電影，雖然近年發展的過程不算順利，但是DC與華納公司仍在努力建構更多蝙蝠俠與相關配角人物的電影，比如即將上映的「小丑」、「猛禽小隊」，和「自殺小隊2」，新任的蝙蝠俠，將由現年33歲的羅伯派汀森接手，相關電影預計在2021年推出。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20190922001934-260408?chdtv</code></pre>"},{"pid":"5bc9c892b45dc3ad32adde53e36f96ca000af994","tid":1588643,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T02:09:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"68fd45233fdaf45a3c4254f28fc0662c0c635c4f","tid":1588643,"uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T02:11:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s3.scoopwhoop.com/anj/alfred/81350470.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3.scoopwhoop.com%2Fanj%2Falfred%2F81350470.png&h=03de4cb8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0e85a3c5822769eaa4aae11c683a5bb82994a4bc","tid":1588643,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T02:13:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://escapematter.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/page-5-8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fescapematter.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F12%2Fpage-5-8.jpg&h=f3c8fea6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c6ab78414019bf30cbd88558960c84d089658c92","tid":1588643,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T02:17:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/3e/80/fa/3e80faf1907b48a2314ec904364458c6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2F3e%2F80%2Ffa%2F3e80faf1907b48a2314ec904364458c6.png&h=9e1e335c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"02f9b7232cb79cc0685e79cf0392ac6b5e979ae2","tid":1588643,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T02:22:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hkcitylife.com/image/data/Art%20and%20Culture/movie/Dark-Knight%20ZZZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkcitylife.com%2Fimage%2Fdata%2FArt%2520and%2520Culture%2Fmovie%2FDark-Knight%2520ZZZ.jpg&h=ab2bc0c2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a3777beddda6eb0c530a9e29f6bb932aebd098a4","tid":1588643,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T05:23:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}